data.description: Welcome to 1800 Harrison St. Located in the Northeast of Philadelphia, Frankford subdivision, walking distance to public transportation and shopping, this home is now available for sale and providing large living areas. Enter into a large living room offering high ceilings , neutral decor , plenty of air light coming through front and side windows . Beautiful Wooden floors are an additional great feature in the living room and  extend to a large formal dining room .  Adjacent to large living areas, a eat-in Kitchen providing plenty  of cabinetry as well counter space.  Kitchen provides access to a fenced in back yard that provides gates to park off street if desired. Conveniently  located in the 1st floor at dining room area is a Powder room. The upper level features three large bedroom with  great closet space  in addition a Hall three piece bathroom. Lower level offers an unfinished basement that would be perfect for storage.
